WEBVTT

00:02:28.303 --> 00:02:30.779
the vote.

00:02:30.803 --> 00:02:33.439
Because they are all rational,
once given the vote,

00:02:33.463 --> 00:02:34.873
they produce good government

00:02:34.897 --> 00:02:37.072
and live happily ever after.

00:02:37.096 --> 00:02:39.991
Paradise on Earth, again.

00:02:40.015 --> 00:02:43.092
Sooner or later, electoral
democracy will be

00:02:43.116 --> 00:02:47.103
the only political system
for all countries and all peoples,

00:02:47.127 --> 00:02:49.567
with a free market to make them all rich.

00:02:49.591 --> 00:02:53.117
But before we get there,
we're engaged in a struggle

00:02:53.141 --> 00:02:54.810
between good and evil.

00:02:54.834 --> 00:02:56.370
(Laughter)

00:02:56.394 --> 00:02:58.608
The good belongs to those
who are democracies

00:02:58.632 --> 00:03:00.823
and are charged with a mission
of spreading it